<SYSCALL>SYS_REBOOT=32 SYS_CHDIR=33 SYS_GETCWD=34</SYSCALL>
<VERIFY>VC-5a..VC-5h: PASS|FAIL — evidence per item</VERIFY>
<SUMMARY>final syscall table, constraint compliance, test results, binary size</SUMMARY>
---/SPECIFICATION---
[[/PHASE_5]]

