[[WIN_CONDITION]]
All 6 phases (0-5) PASS their verification checkpoints with mechanical evidence. Kernel terminal: 20+ commands, tokenizer, tab-completion, history, I/O redirection, pipe, binary <= 32768 bytes. Workstation terminal: multi-tab, color profiles, split pane, ANSI state-machine, scrollback, readline-equivalent. Package system: .deb unpack, SAT resolver with pinned fixtures (cycle/diamond/chain), cycle detection, atomic rollback, signed repo. Bridge: kernel↔userspace command forwarding via Z_UI_CMD_BRIDGE_DATA with 2s timeout, byte-level hex verification. Paged PKG_INFO/PKG_SEARCH with <= 56 byte payloads. Zero constraint violations (C1-C12). Zero new external dependencies. Zero forbidden includes. COMPLIANCE_ENGINE checklist PASS on every C function.
[[/WIN_CONDITION]]